<sect1 id="dir_7742e0808b30ee69050dd8321a97f607_1autotoc_md425">
<title>helios::engine::modules::ui::transform</title><para>UI transform components and positioning systems.</para>
<para>This namespace provides components and systems for viewport-relative positioning of UI elements. Unlike spatial transforms used for 3D scene objects, UI transforms work in screen space coordinates relative to viewports.</para>
</sect1>
